S.FORM: Cameron Gaga kska Meycow ka Cameron, 6 00 N, 12 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 475,440 sq km(hangan na o Tg54) (knlbanga dxgal o 472,710 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 2,730 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 24,360,803 hiyi. Gaga Yaounde ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 20 idas 5 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Cameron ga wada sugan 20.60 ka dxgal qpahan, 41.70 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 37.70 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Paul Biya, pnaah hngkawas1982 idas 11 jiyax 6pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
